source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_00<tab>Houu is expert at weighing lesser evils against greater goods, and would see where you fit into the equation.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_00<tab>ノォヴの育成地のホォウは、冒険者に倒してほしい者がいるようだ。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_01<tab>Houu asks you to defeat Worr the Whalefin, a strategos in thrall to the Coral Tridents. Achieve victory in the FATE “Tail of a Whale” in the Sapsa Spawning Grounds to acquire Worr's coral band, and then present it as proof of your deed to Houu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_01<tab>ホォウから、「珊瑚の銛」に協力する戦頭（いくさがしら）の「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F206A801 /var>」に対抗するよう依頼を受けた。サプサ産卵地で発生するF.A.T.E.『海蛇の末路』に参加し、貢献することで得られる「<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>」を入手しよう。入手した<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>はノォヴの育成地の「ホォウ」に渡そう。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_02<tab>Houu receives the coral band and is greatly impressed by your martial skills. You have apparently made an equally strong impression on other Sahagin. Let us hope they will no longer be so quick to follow the Tridents' incitement to take on shorewalkers in open warfare...
target: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_SEQ_02<tab>ホォウに<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>を渡した。ホォウは冒険者の活躍を、大いに賞賛した。指導者である戦頭と戦ったことで、サハギン族の戦士たちに、人の強さが伝わったことだろう。「珊瑚の銛」をけん制するためにも、武勲を上げていこう。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_TODO_00<tab>Deliver the coral band obtained in the FATE “Tail of a Whale” to Houu.
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_TODO_00<tab>F.A.T.E.「海蛇の末路」に参加して入手した
<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>をホォウに渡す

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Have you heard of the strategoi of the Shhhapsa Shhhpawning Grounds? They are leaders among Shhhahagin warriors, possessed of great influence.
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_000<tab>フスィーッ……「サプサ産卵地」には、
戦頭（いくさがしら）と呼ばれる、戦士たちの長がいる……。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_001<tab>Alas, the Shhhcarlet Shhhea Devil has been inflaming their pride with visions of easy victory. Shhhubtle and shhhly are the Coral Tridents. If nothing is done, their aggression will soon lead to all-out war with you shhhorewalkers...
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_001<tab>その有力者たちを、「珊瑚の銛」のリーダーである、
「紅珊瑚の海魔」が味方につけたようだ……。
このままでは、ヒレナシとの決戦が現実になる……！

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_002<tab>The strategoi must see that the shhhorewalker is a foe shhhkilled and dangerous. You will fight the most boastful among them. Worr the Whalefin is his name, and he must die this day. Pshhh...
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_002<tab>奴らを懲らしめ、その士気を削がないことには……
サハギン族全体が、戦いの渦に巻き込まれかねない。
戦頭のひとり、「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F206A801 /var>」を退けるのだ……。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_003<tab>Worr has a coral band, given him as an ally shhhworn of the Coral Tridents. Bring me this bauble as proof that Worr died as shhhamefully as he lived. Pshhh...
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_003<tab>「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F206A801 /var>」は「珊瑚の銛」の同志の証として……
「<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>」を与えられたらしい……。
奴と戦った証拠として奪い持ち帰るのだ……フスィーッ！

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_010<tab>Pshhh... Shhhlay Worr the Whalefin and seize from him the coral band of the Tridents.
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_010<tab>フスィーッ……「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F206A801 /var>」を退けて、
奴から「<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>」を奪うのだ……。

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_011<tab>Pshhh... Worr's coral band, by all that's indigo! The clutchfather always chooses wisely... Little did I expect a shhhorewalker to best the Whalefin.
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_011<tab>フスィーッ……これはまさしく「<var 28 ((Item)) F21E7C01 /var>」！
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F206A801 /var>」と互角に戦うとは、やはり只者ではないな……。
さすがは、親父の肝入りのヒレナシだ……！

source: TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_012<tab>A strategos is a leader of minds as well as shhhpears. Worr's defeat at a shhhorewalker's hands is an object lesson that will shhhpread throughout the Shhhapsa Shhhpawning Grounds. Pshhh...
target:
TEXT_BANSAH207_01396_HOUU_000_012<tab>戦頭は戦士たちの長であり……指導者だ。
奴らを打ち負かしたことで、産卵地に棲む戦士たちも、
ヒトの強さを思い知ったことだろう……フスィー！
